{"tid":913171,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［荒島求生］請選擇行動：","createTime":"2018-11-23T07:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T17:03:22.000Z","uid":216132,"like":3,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fd7f590dd78bd3f4357b6ad4e523de2d9332fa06","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"你滿嘴都是海水的鹹味，從昏迷中醒來， 陽光刺眼非常，你花了幾秒鐘來適應，察覺眼前是一望無際的海洋。<br />\n<br />\n你發現自己身處一個沙灘，背後是長有椰子樹的樹林，但是一大片都被壓壞了，一條畢直的軌跡延伸了幾百米，遠處還有濃煙冒起。<br />\n<br />\n我到底是誰&hellip;我好像失憶了，接下來應該怎麼做呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 探索沙灘"},{"pid":"5d7fdf73f96e5be8269756ec36e1afe8c8f0eeaf","tid":913171,"uid":116309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"探索沙灘"},{"pid":"30d6e83ca9cd5e1fa9b48273037a8af02d966fb2","tid":913171,"uid":118989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"唔可以探索完沙灘再入森林？"},{"pid":"312bbe4d4a0d90663373c02fec318881404b87da","tid":913171,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:05:57.000Z","msg":"單手遊出公海"},{"pid":"d2494bbe205a8112fc2caf66c2768d3ee288a130","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fd7f590dd78bd3f4357b6ad4e523de2d9332fa06","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"你滿嘴都是海水的鹹味，從昏迷中醒來， 陽光刺眼非常，你花了幾秒鐘來適應，察覺眼前是一望無際的海洋。<br />\n<br />\n你發現自己身處一個沙灘，背後是長有椰子樹的樹林，但是一大片都被壓壞了，一條畢直的軌跡延伸了幾百米，遠處還有濃煙冒起。<br />\n<br />\n我到底是誰&hellip;我好像失憶了，接下來應該怎麼做呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 探索沙灘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VcwVAdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVcwVAdB.jpg&h=e2d884d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmtXOyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkmtXOyB.jpg&h=62bcd0e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1807ab41adf4aa5f32fc4da53b9fb8451fafeb9d","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"fd7f590dd78bd3f4357b6ad4e523de2d9332fa06","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"你滿嘴都是海水的鹹味，從昏迷中醒來， 陽光刺眼非常，你花了幾秒鐘來適應，察覺眼前是一望無際的海洋。<br />\n<br />\n你發現自己身處一個沙灘，背後是長有椰子樹的樹林，但是一大片都被壓壞了，一條畢直的軌跡延伸了幾百米，遠處還有濃煙冒起。<br />\n<br />\n我到底是誰&hellip;我好像失憶了，接下來應該怎麼做呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 探索沙灘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 探索沙灘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DF1a8GO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDF1a8GO.jpg&h=3f7fcd94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有不少破損的行李、袋、衣服、物品等散落一地，陽光火辣，你繼續在沙灘上探索，感到嘴唇像是要乾涸得裂開了。<br />\n<br />\n「謝天謝地！」你在其中一個箱子中，找到了很多在飛機餐派的那種很小兜的水。<br />\n<br />\n你打開了其中幾兜，一飲而盡。 接下來你找到了遮陽帽，沒錯就是大媽去旅行那種，來住陽光。<br />\n<br />\n軌跡末端的黑煙似乎越來越濃烈了。<br />\n<br />\n物品：遮陽帽*1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  繼續探索沙灘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡"},{"pid":"0c44d568c2f9c4140ebddd8d8c3d8b8c683445bc","tid":913171,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"瞬移返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb727b2ed0d350066a01e07afecef85941c65d35","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"接下來你又發現了一些充氣式救生衣，但周圍一個人都沒有就只有救生衣，連腳印都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n然後你又發現了一些衣服、日常用品等等，太可憐了，這些人只是打算去旅行吧， 行李竟然都亂七八糟的沖到這個地方來了&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你敢不住思考到底發生了什麼事，但是一打算用腦就頭痛。<br />\n<br />\n最後你找到了一個手提箱子，但是打開的方式很複雜，你決定暫時先和其他物品放在一起，以後再作打算。<br />\n<br />\n軌跡末端的黑煙似乎越來越濃烈了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XrNtVrR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrNtVrR.png&h=0c2c0cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整理在沙灘上找到的所有物品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡"},{"pid":"a1ec56fcf40bdd7e4d6f537658ebd46557b40059","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"30d6e83ca9cd5e1fa9b48273037a8af02d966fb2","tid":913171,"uid":118989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"唔可以探索完沙灘再入森林？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瞬移返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 單手遊出公海"},{"pid":"1f2ff3853a284f2a0eb27e95861227dcbe0e562e","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"你站在沙灘上沒有做任何事，陽光曬得你的皮膚灼熱，損失了3 HP。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整理在沙灘上找到的所有物品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡"},{"pid":"ab248995baa9e6c2f54c9ff9532178c7bf26f3e3","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"1f2ff3853a284f2a0eb27e95861227dcbe0e562e","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"你站在沙灘上沒有做任何事，陽光曬得你的皮膚灼熱，損失了3 HP。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整理在沙灘上找到的所有物品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整理在沙灘上找到的所有物品<br />\n<br />\n你整理了身邊的物品，物品清單如下：<br />\n遮陽帽<br />\n水一箱（5天量）<br />\n餅乾一箱（3天量）<br />\n衣服15件<br />\n浮潛眼鏡<br />\n神秘的手提箱<br />\n救生衣三件<br />\n<br />\n遙遠處忽然發出一聲巨響，衝擊波將你和周圍散落的物品都吹飛了&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你躺在地上，出現了短暫的耳鳴，好不容易爬了起來，發現森林中有一大片都燒著了，濃煙四起。<br />\n<br />\n似乎是軌跡的源頭有什麼爆炸了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去看看源頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遠離森林去探索海岸線"},{"pid":"8e71e7424b3895207f6bfe99c6288ce727c8ad42","tid":913171,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e41fff722888d8d17b86760d63a6ccf8bf4e6151","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e71e7424b3895207f6bfe99c6288ce727c8ad42","tid":913171,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"1f2ff3853a284f2a0eb27e95861227dcbe0e562e","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"你站在沙灘上沒有做任何事，陽光曬得你的皮膚灼熱，損失了3 HP。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整理在沙灘上找到的所有物品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:14:24.000Z","msg":"留言推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投票玩game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0debd82a00cb8dd03674590ca1bec8c87b03ccb","tid":913171,"uid":222994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f2e266940210f0c1c98a810f8fe8df00a539e030","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0debd82a00cb8dd03674590ca1bec8c87b03ccb","tid":913171,"uid":222994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"Lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465d1ca5bd3e9a2ff11e6df39edc2534553cf566","tid":913171,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"投票都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望唔好又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc584ea558d52dceaf9979b97054ae3562e21df3","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"ab248995baa9e6c2f54c9ff9532178c7bf26f3e3","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"1f2ff3853a284f2a0eb27e95861227dcbe0e562e","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"你站在沙灘上沒有做任何事，陽光曬得你的皮膚灼熱，損失了3 HP。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整理在沙灘上找到的所有物品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進入森林探索軌跡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整理在沙灘上找到的所有物品<br />\n<br />\n你整理了身邊的物品，物品清單如下：<br />\n遮陽帽<br />\n水一箱（5天量）<br />\n餅乾一箱（3天量）<br />\n衣服15件<br />\n浮潛眼鏡<br />\n神秘的手提箱<br />\n救生衣三件<br />\n<br />\n遙遠處忽然發出一聲巨響，衝擊波將你和周圍散落的物品都吹飛了&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你躺在地上，出現了短暫的耳鳴，好不容易爬了起來，發現森林中有一大片都燒著了，濃煙四起。<br />\n<br />\n似乎是軌跡的源頭有什麼爆炸了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去看看源頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遠離森林去探索海岸線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去看看源頭<br />\n<br />\n軌跡沿途的一切都被撞壞了，無論是森林還是土丘，偶然還有散落的行李和金屬碎片。<br />\n<br />\n其中一塊比較大的金屬殘片上面寫著CA。好像是飛機的殘骸吧。<br />\n<br />\n所以這條軌跡都是飛機緊急降落時的衝擊？接下來我看見了幾個脫落的輪子，就是飛機上起落架那種，我更加確定自己的推測。<br />\n<br />\n而我已經不能再前進了，整片森林都著火了&hellip;等等，我好像看見火焰裏有一個女性恫體的人影，是人嗎？有可能在哪種高溫下生存嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 和人影答話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靜觀其變"},{"pid":"ee2c71d8aaac2c20a04348755bb1e0df10935470","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuN2hz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuN2hz8.jpg&h=d84441bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20463e07a34ea5b1fb87bab3c18f3a3ce80a3295","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":11,"dislike":22,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 和人影答話<br />\n<br />\n「你&hellip;沒事嗎？」 我想了半天，只說得出這句話。 畢竟我是一個連登的毒撚，和女生說話實在太尷尬了。<br />\n<br />\n再加上她，可是一個在火焰中都不為所動的女生。<br />\n<br />\n人影注意到我，轉過頭來。<br />\n<br />\n隔著火焰，我似乎看見她的雙眼正在凝視著我。<br />\n<br />\n火勢好像越來越嚴重了，你又損失了 3 HP。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 立即離開以免受到波及<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要求人影和你一起離開"},{"pid":"23eb6c4fe9957336558b68044bcf2f1ec7b94b38","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313876c9fcc332f374b2e71817605e1109c95e0b","tid":913171,"uid":207522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcb42e00f658de034c25dd1076a39e97170f2d9","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"313876c9fcc332f374b2e71817605e1109c95e0b","tid":913171,"uid":207522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"4 vs 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e24775482dd369197063042a48781468ab447e4","tid":913171,"uid":207522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bcb42e00f658de034c25dd1076a39e97170f2d9","tid":913171,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"313876c9fcc332f374b2e71817605e1109c95e0b","tid":913171,"uid":207522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"4 vs 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:12:49.000Z","msg":"我投撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cfd3f2056566664fcaf32a460d5db76768c731","tid":913171,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:16:17.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1806cb7cd9855fd0dac8552d9002f51b6c801d4a","tid":913171,"uid":144645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}